Comment: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:22.78,Ristorante,Sign,0,0,0,,The People of the Ristorante
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.31,0:00:04.73,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I guess it's time\Nto go and try it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:07.27,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Your food for the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.15,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Knock it off already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:12.86,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm not ready to serve it\Nto the owner yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:17.37,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Stop at a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:20.08,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Staying up late is bad\Nfor your complexion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:21.70,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:33.88,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,All right, this looks\Nlike a cinch to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:38.35,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Was that pot there before?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:42.64,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Sure feels good\Nto do a nice deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:44.64,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It was {\i1}her{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:49.07,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Every once in a while she does something that reminds me she's my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:55.95,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:23.33,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I totally forgot that {\i1}her{\i0}\Nbirthday's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:26.45,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We had a party for her\Nhere last year too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:28.62,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Did you receive\Nan invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.96,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:35.67,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It makes sense, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:40.72,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Since she doesn't want the owner to know\Nthat I'm actually her daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:44.72,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I guess she had no choice but to invite me this year, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.31,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,because I came to Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:48.64,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,That's not the case at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:54.52,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's delighted to be able to spend her special day with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.48,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Claudio...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:02:59.20,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:02.24,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Is nine o'clock OK for\NGabrielle's reservation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:05.16,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,That'll be fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:14.00,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I should get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:24.39,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Don't let anyone see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:27.31,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Thank you for preparing\Nthe antipasto for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:31.94,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Claudio and Luciano were the ones behind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:33.56,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:34.81,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Ciao.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:39.11,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We'll be awaiting\Nyour next visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:51.66,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She shouldn't even\Ncome to the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.50,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It's just going to\Nannoy Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.75,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Be more gentle\Nwith the ingredients!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.80,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,There are seven parties\Nbooked for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.63,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,{\a6}One of them is a group\Nfrom Japan, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:06.80,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Claudio said he didn't feel\Nthat way anymore, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.85,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,That ring barely stays on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.48,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sure you haven't\Nlost weight, Claudio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.94,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,My fingers have\Ngotten narrower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.27,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Why not just\Ntake the ring off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:21.44,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We've been through\Nthis before, Vito.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.70,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It's because he can't\Nforget those memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.82,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,That's not why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.53,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Then what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.62,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,See, it's déjà vu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.21,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It's not that he can't forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.50,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,it's that he doesn't\Nwant to forget, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:49.18,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Claudio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.61,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Don't do that\Nlike it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:02.07,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Nicoletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.95,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Still, they sure are late...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.66,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,May I interrupt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.75,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Nicoletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.34,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:22.42,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,This is your dress\Nfor the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:25.17,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I just finished\Nbuying it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.76,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Don't you have work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.59,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I took the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:31.51,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'll get you\Nsomething to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.48,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,One cappuccino, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:39.44,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Should I give you two\Na few minutes to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.27,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I have to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.78,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I thought that\Nmight be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.36,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Here you go, Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:50.49,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I think you know\Nhow Claudio feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:55.25,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That's all in the past.\NThere's nothing to discuss now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:59.58,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Maybe for you,\Nbut not for Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:03.34,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,And don't tell me\Nyou haven't noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:08.18,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Going to the restaurant all the time, even when you know how he feels, is downright cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:17.98,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:20.06,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.77,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Apologize to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:23.94,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:27.61,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:30.07,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,can I still come by\Nonce in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.08,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,The food is just so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:44.29,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Everyone knows Nicoletta\Nhas a crush on Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:47.30,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I feel bad for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:49.47,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Think about\NClaudio's feelings, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.09,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Excuse me, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.14,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.64,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:54.89,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Though,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:57.56,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,you really should\Ntake the ring off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:03.56,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I'm starting to hate\Nmyself for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:05.82,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Luciano is so blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.74,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Claudio!\NGabrielle's on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:15.74,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm going to take a break from the restaurant for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.41,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:19.20,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Want to meet\Nand talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:22.17,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,No, let's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:25.25,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That red-headed girl\Nstopped by earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:26.71,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Nicoletta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.22,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She said it to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:36.76,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That it's cruel for me to go to the restaurant when I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.22,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.73,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:46.32,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:50.24,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She really cares about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:58.66,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What's so wrong with\Nmaking Claudio some pasta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:01.04,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Anyway, come try\Nthis dress on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.79,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What's that pot all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:07.84,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Nothing, really. I was just\Nin a cooking mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.67,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Claudio seemed\Nto really like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:10.55,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:13.59,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He keeps a close\Neye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:18.47,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I think he was impressed at how you approached Gabrielle earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:23.14,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That's my girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:27.52,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,To think you grew up so well even with me not being around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.53,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I really owe it to\Nyour grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.24,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:38.91,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's almost\Nspring here in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:41.25,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Is it still cold there, Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:44.00,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Yeah. But forget that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:48.79,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I heard about Olga's birthday party coming up. You're going, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:52.88,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It's so random.\NShe's never invited me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:55.59,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Just forgive her\Nand let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:58.60,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She thought of you\Nin her own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:00.06,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:08.31,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Every year she'd send me a letter saying how sorry she was for not inviting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.57,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,What are you going\Nto get her, Luciano?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:16.11,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You're gonna ask that and not say what you're getting her yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:21.62,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Have a cup\Nof coffee, Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.16,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.12,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.67,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,A list of those\Ninvited to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:30.09,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You're going to be\Npurely a guest tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:33.63,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,No way! I'm going to\Nbe in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:39.09,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,The Madam will be happier to see you attending as her daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.01,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,A daughter of a close\Nfriend, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:43.06,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Why does Claudio\Nknow that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:48.81,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You aren't wearing the\Ndress I picked out for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:51.48,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But I'm a staff member...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.98,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,All the men are going to\Nbe wearing suits tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.94,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,so I think it's OK if you\Nwear a formal dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:58.36,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Wearing a dress\Nin the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.32,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Teo's not gonna like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:04.04,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,No problem.\NYou'll take the day off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:07.41,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It's a cozy party only for\Nclose friends and family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:10.58,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Then, she'll be\Ncoming too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:11.59,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.42,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Gabrielle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.09,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Doubtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:26.60,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I peeked at the menu before,\Nand it looks fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:29.10,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Go tell her\Nshe should come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.69,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She's your\Ngood friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:34.27,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Ah, Nicoletta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.24,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She's a good girl, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.66,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:46.95,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Let's have a big party here\Nfor her birthday too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:51.67,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm always so busy\Nin November...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:56.67,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I've only ever been able to send a present and a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:11:00.05,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm glad she could\Nbe here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:04.51,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Though, it'd be bad if others found out that she's my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:08.35,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:10.14,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Your ring looks like\Nit's going to come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:14.52,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You should wear a different ring,\Nif it's just to keep the customers at bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.23,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'll get one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:18.99,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:23.62,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You make it so easy to take advantage of you, Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:24.99,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.33,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But you know, Claudio...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:26.95,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:32.62,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Gabrielle isn't the only one\Nwaiting for you to take that ring off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.97,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Is my hair going to be\NOK all flat like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.18,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Oh, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:44.59,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,The pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:52.48,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It's like she just\Ncooked it for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:59.48,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Actually, can she even cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:03.49,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I can't picture her\Nacting like a housewife...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:12.37,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I guess it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:41.32,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You look concerned\Nabout me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.57,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.28,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I won't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:52.12,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'll the keep the fact\NI'm your daughter a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:56.21,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.92,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,The food is a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:04.55,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Isn't it fantastic?\NGigi's eating his fill tonight, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:07.80,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,And we've got extra\Nhelp tonight, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:11.97,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh no, I'm honored to be standing in the same kitchen as Mr. Facchini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:15.31,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,As you're a guest tonight,\Nyou are not to enter the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:17.48,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You don't have to block me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:20.69,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He's blushing because you look so fetching tonight, Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.32,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.53,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You're always quick\Nwith the jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:28.28,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,But she truly is fetching.\NDon't you agree, Claudio?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.70,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:35.91,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Teo, it's about time we\Nbring her dish to the guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.87,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Carry it out, Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:41.42,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What? I-I shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:44.05,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,What? You're so\Nmodest all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:46.68,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,And here I was trying to pay\Nyou your rightful dues.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.76,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.47,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,This is the best meal\Nyou've made so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:55.23,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You did a proper job\Nand put feeling into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.73,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Show some\Nmore confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.86,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:11.95,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you ask\Nsomeone else to do it today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:15.95,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Is she really my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.96,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She's got it together so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:21.21,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Sure it's not because\Nyou didn't raise her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.25,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:26.88,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I've got to be one of\Nthe worst mothers alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:28.84,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You {\i1}were{\i0} one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:32.85,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But now, she's close by\Nand really looks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:37.10,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,A girl moving on from\Nher mother is a huge deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:41.56,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She's going to become a charming lady right by your side now, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:48.90,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Tanti auguri a te.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:52.41,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Tanti auguri a te.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:51.87,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Lorenzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:56.87,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Tanti auguri a Olga...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:15:01.00,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Tanti auguri a te.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.83,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,My, it looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:06.42,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Nicoletta made this cake\Nfor you. She said it's a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:34.74,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I have a confession to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:39.16,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,My daughter, Nicoletta,\Nmade this cake for me as a gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:39.79,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.67,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I had her with\Nmy ex-husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.96,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I apologize for keeping it\Nsecret all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.51,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I didn't want to be rejected,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:53.68,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,so I just kept on lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:55.43,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:00.68,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:01.94,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:06.52,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I knew she was your daughter\Nsoon after she started working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:08.44,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You have the same smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:11.44,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I wondered why you\Nnever said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:15.28,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But, Lorenzo, you said you don't like women with kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:18.62,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sure, I'd have preferred that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:23.87,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,But, I'll welcome her with open arms,\Nif she's your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:36.85,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.35,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:45.60,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I just get to be\Na selfish brat for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:49.69,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Anyway, blow out the candles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:52.36,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.11,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll carry those.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.57,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.49,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.41,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That was anticlimactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:43.95,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I didn't think the owner\Nwas the type to reject her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.96,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,and turns out I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:51.13,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But, I also understand what it's like to be a woman frantically in love and afraid of rejection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:56.22,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I don't want to\Nbe rejected either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.22,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You're in luck, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:09.27,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:34.00,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Olga really seems like\Nshe's made up for lost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:37.05,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It's like revealing her daughter has given her new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:38.88,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,How are things\Nat the restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:41.34,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,She's continuing on\Nas an apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:43.81,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Luciano still scolds her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:47.81,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,So, what did you\Nwant to see me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:02.16,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sorry it took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:07.08,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Have you responded\Nto her feelings for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:09.00,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.04,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.79,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We're still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:17.09,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Come by the\Nrestaurant sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.56,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,All right, here's a little extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:33.02,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.90,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Oh, Claudio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:36.90,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:39.32,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,No way, my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.65,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:41.61,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Nicoletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:44.62,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sorry, she misspoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.37,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Are you out\Nshopping too, Claudio?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:50.16,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll carry your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:52.00,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.09,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Anything else you\Nwant to check out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.38,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Claudio...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.55,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Are you free today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:05.47,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I usually relax at home\Non my days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:07.06,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Wanna come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:08.43,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'll make you\Nsomething good to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.39,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:13.39,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,All right. Carry those\Nbags to my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:24.99,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I wonder if the regulars will be able to tell we're an item.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:29.24,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I feel like I won somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:37.38,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,OK, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:46.51,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Its name is casetta dell'orso.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:51.81,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,If you ever find yourself\Nin Rome, go look for it...